你能够调用以下的API:
[['PolygonFinance.get_ticker_news', {'name': 'PolygonFinance.get_ticker_news', 'description': 'get the most recent news articles relating to a stock ticker symbol', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [{'name': 'ticker', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'Return results that contain this ticker'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'results', 'description': 'A list of news including title, summary, and author'}]}], ['SocialMediaAnalytics.get_social_media_discussion', {'name': 'SocialMediaAnalytics.get_social_media_discussion', 'description': 'Retrieve the discussion volume and sentiment on social media platforms for a given stock ticker over a specified time period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'ticker', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock ticker symbol.'}, {'name': 'time_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time period for which to retrieve discussions (e.g., 1 year, 6 months).'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'discussion_volume', 'description': 'The volume of discussions.'}, {'name': 'sentiment_score', 'description': 'The sentiment score of the discussions.'}]}], ['StockMarketAPI.get_stock_price_history', {'name': 'StockMarketAPI.get_stock_price_history', 'description': 'Retrieve the historical stock prices for a given ticker over a specified time period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'ticker', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock ticker symbol.'}, {'name': 'time_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time period for which to retrieve prices (e.g., 1 year, 6 months).'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'price_history', 'description': 'A list of historical prices including date and price.'}]}], ['StockMarketAPI.get_real_time_stock_price', {'name': 'StockMarketAPI.get_real_time_stock_price', 'description': 'Retrieve the current stock price for a given ticker.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'ticker', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock ticker symbol.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'current_price', 'description': 'The current stock price.'}]}], ['InvestorSentimentAnalysis.analyze_investor_sentiment', {'name': 'InvestorSentimentAnalysis.analyze_investor_sentiment', 'description': 'Analyze the investor sentiment based on news, social media discussions, and stock price data.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'news_data', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The API used to retrieve news data.'}, {'name': 'social_media_data', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The API used to retrieve social media data.'}, {'name': 'price_history', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The API used to retrieve historical price data.'}, {'name': 'real_time_price', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The API used to retrieve real-time price data.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'sentiment_score', 'description': 'The overall sentiment score.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
